    <name>Module Goals</name>
    <intro></intro>
    <introformat>1</introformat>
    <content>&lt;p dir="ltr" style="text-align: left;"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/Goals.png" alt="Target" width="120" height="125" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_right"&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul role="list"&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="1" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b4c8dcfd-066c-454c-8936-e0c90a21acac}{24}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Purpose:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;The purpose of this module is to improve the learning&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;experience for all adult learners, including those with learning differences by&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;improving how&amp;nbsp;you design and cultivate community in your classrooms.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="2" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b4c8dcfd-066c-454c-8936-e0c90a21acac}{27}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.13999,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Your Task:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;Your task is to consider how you currently build community and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;then reflect on the content in this module to identify how you could design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;learning experiences that are&amp;nbsp;authentic and relevant to adult learners.&lt;/span&gt;​&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li data-aria-posinset="3" role="listitem" data-aria-level="1"&gt;&lt;p xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US" paraid="0" paraeid="{b4c8dcfd-066c-454c-8936-e0c90a21acac}{30}" data-ccp-props="{&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559683&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559731&amp;quot;:-230,&amp;quot;335559737&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335562764&amp;quot;:2,&amp;quot;335562765&amp;quot;:1.14,&amp;quot;335562766&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562767&amp;quot;:6,&amp;quot;335562768&amp;quot;:4,&amp;quot;335562769&amp;quot;:6}"&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrap&amp;nbsp;Up:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;During the final sections of this module, you will be asked to&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;review&amp;nbsp;your initial understanding by comparing what you thought first&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to&amp;nbsp;what you think now. Through this experience you will be better equipped&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;to build learning experiences, where&amp;nbsp;adult learners enjoy a sense of&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;belonging, and can access&amp;nbsp;information and apply it to solve problems that&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-usefontface="false" data-contrast="none" xml:lang="EN-US" lang="EN-US"&gt;are&amp;nbsp;important to them.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 1.7rem;"&gt;&lt;img src="@@PLUGINFILE@@/divider-wave-1.png" alt="" width="1920" height="195" role="presentation" class="img-responsive atto_image_button_text-bottom"&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</content>
